        SELECT 1
        FROM [AbpSettings] AS [a]
        WHERE (([a].[Name] = @__name_0) AND [a].[TenantId] IS NULL) AND [a].[UserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    ELSE [t].[TenancyName]

ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

    ELSE [t].[TenancyName]

    FROM [AbpTenants] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [a].[TenantId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE 0 = 1
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'.'
    ELSE [t].[TenancyName]
END, [a].[UserName]

OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
